## 🎯 **Capstone Project Ideas**

- 🤖 Build an AI chatbot for FAQs  
- 🖼️ Make an AI-generated storybook  
- 📜 Create a collection of advanced prompts  
- 🔗 Deploy a prompt-powered app on GitHub

---

## 🚀 **Tips to Succeed**

✔️ **Practice daily:** Small prompts, big ideas  
✔️ **Save your best:** Document prompts & results  
✔️ **Showcase work:** Use GitHub, Notion, or a blog  
✔️ **Stay updated:** Follow AI news & tools

